<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Admin Account Verification - MEDH Foundation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .header .subtitle {
      margin: 5px 0 0 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .admin-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .welcome-text {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #2d3748;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .otp-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7fafc 0%, #edf2f7 100%);
      border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .otp-label {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #4a5568;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #667eea;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 2px dashed #667eea;
    }
    .expiry-notice {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fed7d7 0%, #feb2b2 100%);
      border-left: 4px solid #e53e3e;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .expiry-notice strong {
      color: #c53030;
    }
    .admin-info {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e6fffa 0%, #b2f5ea 100%);
      border-left: 4px solid #38b2ac;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .admin-info h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #2c7a7b;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .admin-details {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #2d3748;
    }
    .admin-details div {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    .security-notice {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef5e7 0%, #fed7aa 100%);
      border: 1px solid #f6ad55;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .security-notice .icon {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f7fafc;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #718096;
      padding: 25px 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #667eea;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .help-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #718096;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f7fafc;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üîê MEDH Foundation</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Admin Portal Access</p>
      <div class="admin-badge">
        üëë ADMIN REGISTRATION
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="welcome-text">
        Hello {{name}},
      </div>
      
      <p>Welcome to the MEDH Foundation Admin Portal! Your admin account registration is almost complete.</p>
      
      {{#if department}}
      <div class="admin-info">
        <h3>üìã Admin Account Details</h3>
        <div class="admin-details">
          <div><strong>Name:</strong> {{name}}</div>
          <div><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</div>
          {{#if department}}<div><strong>Department:</strong> {{department}}</div>{{/if}}
          {{#if designation}}<div><strong>Designation:</strong> {{designation}}</div>{{/if}}
          {{#if admin_role}}<div><strong>Admin Role:</strong> {{admin_role}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/if}}
      
      <p>To complete your admin account setup and gain access to the admin dashboard, please verify your email address using the verification code below:</p>
      
      <div class="otp-section">
        <div class="otp-label">Admin Verification Code</div>
        <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #718096; margin-top: 10px;">
          Enter this code in the admin verification page
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="expiry-notice">
        <strong>‚è∞ Time Sensitive:</strong> This verification code will expire in <strong>{{expiryMinutes}} minutes</strong> for security purposes.
      </div>
      
      <div class="security-notice">
        <span class="icon">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
        <strong>Security Notice:</strong> This is a secure admin registration. If you did not request admin access to MEDH Foundation, please contact our security team immediately.
      </div>
      
      <p>After verification, you will have access to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>üìä Admin Dashboard</li>
        <li>üë• User Management</li>
        <li>üìö Course Management</li>
        <li>üìà Analytics & Reports</li>
        <li>‚öôÔ∏è System Settings</li>
      </ul>
      
      <div class="help-text">
        <strong>Need Help?</strong><br>
        If you're having trouble with verification or have questions about your admin account, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@medh.co">support@medh.co</a>
      </div>
      
      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
        Best regards,<br>
        <strong>The MEDH Foundation Team</strong><br>
        <em>Admin Portal Security</em>
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} MEDH Foundation. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This admin verification email was sent to <strong>{{email}}</strong></p>
      <p>
        <a href="https://medh.co/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> | 
        <a href="https://medh.co/terms">Terms of Service</a> | 
        <a href="mailto:support@medh.co">Support</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
